2. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper studies the distributed OR algorithm as an abstract of the system, which falls under the domain of distributed computing. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses lower bounds of anonymity leakage, which is related to information theory. 
4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication systems and their properties, which is a key area of research in networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the relationship between the model and some open cases in the study of secret sharing scheme, which is related to systems and control.
